OL,3,GNorthern Ireland
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA settled
OL,6,Fevening with some late sunshine. Cloud
OL,7,Fwill then increase through the night
OL,8,Fto bring the risk of patchy rain in
OL,9,Fthe early hours.
OL,10,
OL,11,CWednesday:FA largely cloudy morning
OL,12,Fwith patchy light rain which may
OL,13,Flinger in the west. The best of the
OL,14,Fdrier and brighter conditions will be
OL,15,Fin east with some afternoon sunshine.
OL,16,
OL,17,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:FA
OL,18,Fgood deal of cloud around during this
OL,19,Fperiod with showers, but some brighter
OL,20,Fperiods. Rather breezy at times.
